MAPPING.DESCRIPTION:
Dimension transformation for D_ProductDet.
Transforms gaming machine games from mac_config by identifying unique combinations of Game Code and Denomination.
MAPPING.NAME: m_ProductDet_EGM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.ext_code, S_DACOM_Mac_Config.game_code, S_DACOM_Mac_Config.denomination, uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_N.c_long, S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum FROM S_DACOM_Mac_Config, uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_N, uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M , S_DACOM_Device WHERE S_DACOM_Device.device_id = S_DACOM_Mac_Config.device_id AND uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.c_short = S_DACOM_Device.manufacturer AND uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_N.c_short = S_DACOM_Mac_Config.game_code and S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum = S_DACOM_Device.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum = uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum =uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_N.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum = $$Property_no ORDER BY uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.ext_code, S_DACOM_Mac_Config.game_code, S_DACOM_Mac_Config.denomination

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: User Defined Join
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: S_DACOM_Device.device_id = S_DACOM_Mac_Config.device_id AND S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.c_short = S_DACOM_Device.manufacturer AND S_DACOM_Class_Code_N.c_short = S_DACOM_Mac_Config.game_code and S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum = S_DACOM_Device.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum = uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum =uvw_S_DACOM_Class_Code_N.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum = $$Property_no

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT D_PRODUCTDET.PRODUCTDETID as PRODUCTDETID, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.GAMENAME) as GAMENAME, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.SUBGAMENAME) as SUBGAMENAME, D_PRODUCTDET.JACKPOTFLG as JACKPOTFLG, D_PRODUCTDET.EGMLines as EGMLines, D_PRODUCTDET.RwrdLvl as RwrdLvl,D_PRODUCTDET.EdgeTheo as EdgeTheo, D_PRODUCTDET.TblMaxBet as TblMaxBet, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.AltGamingActvyCde) as AltGamingActvyCde, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.AltSubGameCde) as AltSubGameCde, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.AltSubGameName) as AltSubGameName, D_PRODUCTDET.SctyCde as SctyCde, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.GameTyp) as GameTyp, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.GAMINGPRODTYP) as GAMINGPRODTYP, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.GAMINGACTIVITYCODE) as GAMINGACTIVITYCODE, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.EGM_GAMECODE) as EGM_GAMECODE, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.EGM_DENOM) as EGM_DENOM, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.SUBGAMECODE) as SUBGAMECODE, D_PRODUCTDET.TBLMINBET as TBLMINBET, D_PRODUCTDET.TBLLVL as TBLLVL, D_PRODUCTDET.SiteID as SiteID FROM D_PRODUCTDET where D_PRODUCTDET.SiteID in (1,2)

[15/04/2014 LK]Modify to add null value for GameTyp

15/16 Jun 2005 Stephen Tyler , DWS What 1. Changed subgamecode and subgamename calculations to cater for multi games 2. Change default for JACKPOTFLG, AltGamingActvyCde, AltSubGameCde, AltSubGameName to null from a question mark 3. Change defaults for RwrdLvl, EdgeTheo and TblMaxBet from zero to null 4. Changed subgamename calc to look up on subgamecode rater than gamecode. Why 1. Not previously captured 2,3. No longer a not null field and supposed to be null 4. Advice from Andrew Wylie, 16 Jun
[11 April 2005 Stephen Tyler, DWS] Reinstated original SQL query for source qualifier - refer comments 23 March 2005

Amended calculation of v_EGM_GAMECODE in Exp_TransformTargets from SUBSTR(S_DACOM_Mac_Config_game_code, 4,7) to SUBSTR(S_DACOM_Mac_Config_game_code, 4,10). This agrees with calc used in Gaming Machine Config mapping
[23 March 2005 Stephen Tyler]
Amended SQL query for source qualifier. Required purely for system testing due to file format problems. Will need to be replaced with the following original SQL Query once file format fixed:
SELECT DISTINCT S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.ext_code, S_DACOM_Mac_Config.game_code, S_DACOM_Mac_Config.denomination, S_DACOM_Class_Code_N.c_long FROM S_DACOM_Mac_Config, S_DACOM_Class_Code_N, S_DACOM_Class_Code_M , S_DACOM_Device WHERE S_DACOM_Device.device_id = S_DACOM_Mac_Config.device_id AND S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.c_short = S_DACOM_Device.manufacturer AND S_DACOM_Class_Code_N.c_short = S_DACOM_Mac_Config.game_code ORDER BY S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.ext_code, S_DACOM_Mac_Config.game_code, S_DACOM_Mac_Config.denomination
